MSRPWorker - Class in com.mobixell.xtt
MSRPWorker Processes a single MSRP request which has been received by the MSRPServer Copyright: Copyright (c) 2007 Company: 724 Solutions Inc Stores headers as
Response:
MSRP/[serverport]/RESPONSE/[transactionid]
MSRP/[serverport]/RESPONSE/[messageiid]
MSRP/[serverport]/RESPONSE
MSRP/RESPONSE/[transactionid]
MSRP/RESPONSE/[messageiid]
MSRP/RESPONSE
and:
/HEADER/[headername]
/CODE
/MESSAGE
/TRANSACTIONID
Request:
MSRP/[serverport]/[METHOD]/[transactionid]
MSRP/[serverport]/[METHOD]/[messageiid]
MSRP/[serverport]/[METHOD]
MSRP/[METHOD]/[transactionid]
MSRP/[METHOD]/[messageiid]
MSRP/[METHOD]
MSRP/REQUEST and:
/HEADER/[headername]
/BODY/BASE64
/BODY/PLAIN
/FIRSTLINE
/METHOD
/TRANSACTIONID

The Variable ending in /FINISHED/REQUEST is set to true after sending the response/finishing the response handling.

RTSPWorker - Class in com.mobixell.xtt
RTSPWorker Processes a single RTSP request which has been received by the RTSPServer Copyright: Copyright (c) 2007 Company: 724 Solutions Inc Stores headers as
Response:
RTSP/[port]/RESPONSE/[sessionid]/
RTSP/[port]/RESPONSE/
RTSP/[port]/TCP/RESPONSE/[sessionid]/
RTSP/[port]/TCP/RESPONSE/
RTSP/TCP/RESPONSE/[sessionid]/
RTSP/TCP/RESPONSE/
and:
/HEADER/[headername]
/BODY/BASE64
/BODY/PLAIN

Request:
RTSP/[port]/[method]/[sessionid]/
RTSP/[port]/[method]/[url]/
RTSP/[port]/[method]/
RTSP/[port]/TCP/[method]/[sessionid]/
RTSP/[port]/TCP/[method]/[url]/
RTSP/[port]/TCP/[method]/
RTSP/TCP/[method]/[sessionid]/
RTSP/TCP/[method]/[url]/
RTSP/TCP/[method]/
and:
/HEADER/[headername]
/BODY/BASE64
/BODY/PLAIN

The Variable ending in /FINISHED/REQUEST is set to true after sending the response/finishing the response handling.

Creates a new RTSPWorker
